.TH wxControlWithItems 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxControlWithItems \- This is convenience class that derives from both \fIwxControl\fR and \fIwxItemContainer\fR (not implemented in wx).

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
It is used as basis for some wxWidgets controls (\fIwxChoice\fR and \fIwxListBox\fR).

.PP
This class is derived, and can use functions, from:


.sp
